column3: even C-3PO becoming a shadow of his brilliant self. The new characters are just not empathy inspiring perhaps John Boyega\'s Finn is the closest but definitely getting lost through the plot. At least by "joining the force" the old & petty Luke Skywalker is saving face from appearing in the next sequel. '
